summary: ...GABRIELLE RACING EASTWARD TOWARD THE AZORES... ...EXPECTED TO BRING HURRICANE CONDITIONS TO THE AZORES TONIGHT OR EARLY FRIDAY... As of 12:00 PM GMT Thu Sep 25 the center of Gabrielle was located near 36.4, -36.5 with movement E at 32 mph. The minimum central pressure was 980 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 85 mph.
